title: Made In Chelsea S08E02 HDTV x264 TVCUK
description:
Andy Jordan is busy expressing how he feels about his ex-girlfriend Louise finding love in New York, but it's not well received by her new beau Alik. Louise doesn't have much time before an explosive revelation threatens to tear Chelsea's newest couple apart. Lucy and Proudlock finally have a first date, which they had vowed to keep a secret, but in true Chelsea style the news spreads like wildfire. Meanwhile, another romance is on the cards as fitness instructor Will limbers up to woo Binky.
